import React, { Component } from 'react' // import search from '../' import './index.sass' import logic from '../../logic' class Results extends Component{ state={redirect:false} onDetails=event=>{ event.preventDefault(); } render() { const user= JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem('user')) const maxCalories= logic.caloriesCounter(user.gender, user.height, user.weight, user.birthDate, user.lifeStyle) console.log(maxCalories) const { recipes } = this.props return
{ recipes.map(recipe => (
{recipe.recipe.label}

{(((recipe.recipe.calories/ recipe.recipe.yield) / maxCalories)*100).toFixed(2) + '%'}

Total time: {recipe.recipe.totalTime}
Go to recipe
)) }
} } export default Results
